<p class="ql-align-center">《湘菜》杂志总编辑刘国初发表致辞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201113/5954d464a1544e469661a4037d9a3746.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">图注：第十一届、第十二届全国人大代表、</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">湘菜泰斗许菊云大师揭晓年度经典湘菜名单</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201113/97cf99796b6f4f1bb956e1d734abc9d2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">图注：冰火楼酒店董事长胡艳萍在发布会现场</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>冰火楼原汁鸡荣获大奖</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">冰火楼22年经典产品【冰火原汁鸡】</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以“源头正宗好食材、</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">新鲜供应不隔夜、</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">坚持不放一粒味精”的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“健康湘菜”为产品理念，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">荣获“年度经典湘菜”奖项。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201113/2798d62f9a834ac78630b8e25831b943.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">图注：获奖企业领奖</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201113/510a8442930b4c149f47de87766abd2f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">图注：冰火楼董事长胡艳萍女士登台领奖并发表讲话</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201113/2c61f88f896b4a2cb69d72dab13ce94e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">图注：冰火楼大厨李祥庭在颁奖现场</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201113/8ba4e8e9535a42a393154418a22b4c3c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">图注：冰火楼大厨李祥庭在现场烹饪原汁鸡，媒体争相采访</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>冰火原汁鸡</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鸡的做法，数不胜数。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而原汁鸡的制作，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最为考验食材的品质与厨师的手艺。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">冰火楼畅销二十二年的原汁鸡，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让人念念不忘的秘诀是什么？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201113/3ed20145801e4ad1ae0ec357e07506ac.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>首先是食材的新鲜。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">冰火楼严选饲养期大于130天的优质整鸡，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">凌晨两三点宰杀好，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当日直送店里，绝不隔夜。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从最大程度上锁住鸡肉的新鲜，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">更加完美地还原其本身的原汁原味。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>其次是腌制。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">冰火楼二十二年精制配方，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">既能提升鸡肉的香味，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">又不掩盖鸡肉本身的鲜味。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">每味调料的配比非常苛刻，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以追求出品把控的严密。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201113/1b0550c916ab4a7cbcb14cd6bf9b5835.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">配好腌料后，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">师傅耐心将腌料仔细涂抹；</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而后加入陈年花雕，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">起到保湿、去腥、提鲜的效果。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">酒性柔和、色泽清亮的花雕</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是腌料的最佳拍档。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201113/403db4dcb6a043fa9905c032d8914556.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>之后便是按摩。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">冰火楼师傅按摩手法了得。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当浸入腌料的整只鸡，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">被师傅舒舒服服地按摩一番后，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">皮肉不但完全放松下来，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">并且不失原本的紧致，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">肌肉脂肪也沉积适度，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">达到了更佳的肉质与口感。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201113/641cdbdaef9e42458b202c8c789586e1.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>最后是无水干蒸。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无水干蒸才能最大程度地</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">保证整只鸡的味、形与营养，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最终达到“阴阳调剂，以水渗热”的效果，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">纯正而健康。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">长达四个小时的干蒸，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">仿佛一场慢慢悠闲的SPA，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">将鸡肉的鲜味提到顶点。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201113/7263278840144b81b716237b139cf0ae.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">经过宰、腌、揉、蒸</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一只冰火楼原汁鸡就做好了。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201113/24354f3767a044a2bf2794ef53ce9545.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蒸出来的鸡肉，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鲜滑纯香，汁水饱满。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">外表极美，皮黄肉白。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">水晶般光滑晶莹的鸡皮，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">金灿灿地泛着光泽。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鸡肉弹嫩，光泽如玉。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鸡骨边渗出一层黄澄澄的鸡油，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">惹人生津。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201113/f633c88bc7b94cf582da8bb088de2f77.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>吃起来，皮薄，肉嫩，味鲜。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">夹起一块鸡肉，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">黄澄澄的皮脂薄薄一层，带着鲜甜；</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">咬下，鸡肉滑嫩，汁水充盈得在嘴里溅开；</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不仅皮爽肉滑，连骨头都有滋味，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">吸吮鸡骨，鲜美得让人欲罢不能。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">汤汁色泽醇厚，吸熘一口，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不禁感叹鸡汤竟能被吊得如此鲜美。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">食后，唇齿留香，方觉喉腔甘润。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201113/b917576541e6478dbe72ca00d1f81e5f.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这就是冰火楼原汁鸡——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>鲜香味美，美容养颜，</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>清润滋补，低脂更健康。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">22年来，冰火楼一直坚持匠心打造健康湘菜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“好食材做更好的美食”是我们不变的初心</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">产品不添加味精</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从田头到餐桌保障舌尖上的食品安全</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">冰火楼在传承与创新中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">用良心与道德一心一意做好菜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">能够荣获此次大奖</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">感恩、感谢、感激！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我们将不负众望，砥砺前行</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为大家带来更好的健康湘菜</p>